ecoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16.jpg\" alt=\"A modern building with cloud-shaped openings.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16-940x940.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-building-cloud-like-cutout-balcony-120525-123-16-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe interiors are defined by a neutral palette and clean materials, with multifunctional furniture, like built-in benches, wardrobes, and storage units, integrated seamlessly with structural elements such as minimalist wooden staircases and lightweight steel-framed floors topped with cement boards.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1913\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17.jpg\" alt=\"A small apartment with a loft bedroom.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17.jpg 1913w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17-940x1258.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-17-1530x2048.jpg 1530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1913px) 100vw, 1913px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1847\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18.jpg\" alt=\"A small apartment with a loft bedroom.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18.jpg 1847w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18-940x1303.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18-800x1109.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18-768x1064.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18-1108x1536.jpg 1108w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/small-micro-apartment-interior-loft-bed-120525-123-18-1478x2048.jpg 1478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1847px) 100vw, 1847px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAt night, the cloud-shaped openings are highlighted by the interior lights of the building.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-apartment-building-cloud-cut-outs-120525